# Network / power / polkit
# lxpolkit must be listed BEFORE network-manager-applet and
# nm-connection-editor: those have a virtual Depends on polkit-1-auth-agent
# and if no provider is installed yet, apt's solver picks `cinnamon` from
# the alternatives list, dragging in the whole desktop. lxpolkit declares
# `Provides: polkit-1-auth-agent` and is the lightest GTK3 agent in Debian.
# (hyprpolkitagent would be the natural choice for Hyprland, but its
# Debian package is missing both `Provides: polkit-1-auth-agent` and
# `Depends: polkitd` — file upstream and revisit when fixed.)
lxpolkit
network-manager
network-manager-tui
network-manager-applet
nm-connection-editor
